title: Ike's Place
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, American, Fast food, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Casual sandwich shop with flagship location in San Francisco; formerly known as Ike's Lair. Has vegetarian and vegan sandwiches using various faux meats like tofurkey, breaded chickn patties, meatballs, plus Daiya vegan cheese. The wheat bread contains honey.
